'''Ally Donaldson''' (born 27 November 1943) is a Scottish former [[association football|footballer]] who played for [[Tynecastle F.C.|Tynecastle]], [[Dundee F.C.|Dundee]], [[Falkirk F.C.|Falkirk]], [[Hibernian F.C.|Hibernian]] and [[Raith Rovers F.C.|Raith Rovers]], as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.neilbrown.newcastlefans.com/player11/allydonaldson.htm |title=Ally Donaldson |accessdate=26 August 2015|publisher=Post War English & Scottish Football League A - Z Player's Transfer Database}}</ref>

